- Complete Hotel Booking System.
- Room Management.
- Bookings Management.
- Customer Management.
- Coupon Management.
- Pricing Plans Management.
- Extra Packages Management.
- Block Special Date Management.
- Report + Multilingual Ready.
- 4 Payment Gateways (Offline Payment, Authorize.Net, PayPal, Stripe).

